    <div class="main review-item" id="1085073">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1085073/" class="title-link">一本津津乐道于细枝末节的传记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1085073"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lzr1996/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1262599-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lzr1996/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">远在江湖</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-10-26"
      class="main-meta">2006-10-26 20:29:49</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1085073_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                     很后悔买了这本书。虽然译的不错，文笔很好，看得很舒服，甚至有些引人入胜，但还是实在是不值得一看。至少49年后的部分不值一看。是不是外国人写的就更可信？就没有意识形态的立场？我看西方人也有立场。将毛泽东从“神”变成“人”就是更好？什么是人性的，往往弄成了七情...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1085073/#comments">(15回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
