  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1121724">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1121724/" class="title-link">简评毛泽东</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1121724"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/wensu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1045798-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/wensu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">哲人之石</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-02-08"
      class="main-meta">2007-02-08 22:46:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1121724_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    在中国近现代史的链条上，毛泽东是一个崭新的环节。从清王朝，到袁世凯和北洋军阀，再到蒋介石，中国社会缓慢而艰难地走向进步。中国革命的胜利，是一代人理想的胜利。然而历史进化的规律是无情的，自然界没有飞跃，人类社会也一样。毛泽东也带有历史的包袱和遗产，他的英雄...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1121724/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 6没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1121724_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1121724_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
